data.description: NEW PRICE! GORGEOUS HOME WITH EVERYTHING YOU NEED TO MAKE YOUR RETIREMENT PERFECT. 2 bedroom, 2.5 bath plus oversized den. Master bath has large walk in shower. Guest bedroom features en suite bathroom. Garage is extended by 4' allowing more room for oversized vehicles while the epoxy floor coating keeps your home cleaner. The landscaping has been thoughtfully designed to create a serene oasis, providing privacy and tranquility. Imagine spending leisurely afternoons relaxing on the patio, enjoying the vibrant colors of the blooming flowers and the soothing sounds of nature.
